Description

Main class for the Moorhuhn game application.

Controller for the main menu of the game, handling user interactions for starting the game, viewing the leaderboard, and more.

Manages music playback for the game, including loading a playlist and playing tracks in sequence.
PlayerInfo
Manages player information including the nickname and weapons inventory.
ScoreEntry
Represents a score entry in the game, containing the player's nickname, score, and position.
ScoreManager
Manages saving and loading of scores and money for the game.
ShopController
Controller for the in-game shop, managing the display and purchase of weapons.
Sounds
Manages sound effects for the game, including gunshot, no ammo, and reload sounds.
Weapon
Represents a weapon in the game, handling ammunition, reloading, and shooting.
WeaponData
Represents the data for a weapon in the game, including its name, cost, status, description, ammo capacity, and reload time.
